00:40:47,220 --> 00:40:47,970
Today,

903
00:40:48,570 --> 00:40:49,770
you're doomed to die.

904
00:41:06,510 --> 00:41:07,240
Mr. Tang,

905
00:41:08,250 --> 00:41:09,650
I want to find Chuanxiang

906
00:41:10,710 --> 00:41:11,480
and ask him

907
00:41:12,360 --> 00:41:13,690
why he wanted to kill me.

908
00:41:17,150 --> 00:41:19,920
