916
00:41:56,510 --> 00:41:57,640
into bitter enemies

917
00:41:57,880 --> 00:42:00,440
and make family members
betray and kill each other.

918
00:42:00,440 --> 00:42:02,480
Who can resist the temptation

919
00:42:02,530 --> 00:42:03,960
of overnight wealth, glory,

920
00:42:03,960 --> 00:42:05,880
